# MinIO RBAC

Automates MinIO user, policy, and bucket management on OpenShift.  
No Ansible. No ArgoCD. No manual UI clicks.

---

## How it works

```
minio-users.yaml  +  minio-secrets.yaml
          ↓
      minio-setup.py
          ↓
  MinIO (buckets, policies, users)
```

- Policies are defined once and shared across many users
- Users run in parallel — 10 or 20 users takes the same time as 1
- Safe to re-run anytime — nothing gets duplicated

---

## Files

```
minio-rbac/
├── minio-setup.py          # the script
├── minio-users.yaml        # users, policies, buckets — commit this
├── minio-secrets.yaml      # passwords + admin creds — never commit
├── minio-setup-job.yaml    # OpenShift Job
├── Dockerfile              # packages baked in (no internet needed)
├── requirements.txt        # minio==7.2.9, pyyaml==6.0.1
└── .gitignore              # excludes minio-secrets.yaml
```

