## Access levels

| Level | List | Download | Upload | Delete |
|-------|------|----------|--------|--------|
| `readonly` | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| `writeonly` | ✅ | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |
| `readwrite` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| `listonly` | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |

