## Local usage

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python minio-setup.py
```

---

## Adding a new user

1. Add to `minio-users.yaml`
2. Add password to `minio-secrets.yaml`
3. Run the script
4. Commit only `minio-users.yaml`

